            <lg xml:id="TK1177">
<l>uḻantuḻan tuṇṇī raṟuka viḻaintiḻaintu </l>
<l> vēṇṭi yavarkaṇṭa kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eyes that became tender and gazed intently on him, may they suffer so much as to dry up the fountain of their tears.</l>
            </lg>
